<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Santayana on Fanaticism</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Mar 09, 2015 00:00</p>
</header> <blockquote class="bigquote">
 <p>
Fanaticism consists in redoubling your efforts when you have forgotten your aim.
</p>
</blockquote>

 <p class="bigquote">
George Santayana,  <i>Reason in Common Sense</i>, Vol. I
</p>


